PURPOSE:
  This module and directory structure is to contain the sources of any project
  documentation that is authored in a structured plain text format.

GUIDELINES:
  There will be more instructions here in the future.  But a definite no-no
  would be checking in documentation created with a WYSIWYG editor that does
  not respect such concepts as a line by line diff.

  Binary documentation, such as MSWord documents (god forbid), is absolutely
  forbidden unless otherwise approved by the project administrator.
